&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Respiratory Community Specialist Nurse&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;An exciting opportunity has arisen to join an award winning integrated community respiratory for either an experienced band 7 or someone who feels they are ready to step up into this role with support.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We would welcome applications for this exciting post from suitable candidates who could be:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A current band 7 nurse&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;An experienced band 6 who is ready to step up to a band 7 role, Or&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A band 6 nurse who could work towards a band 7 with supported development from our team within 2 years. Respiratory experience is essential for all of the above and acute care experience would be desirable.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;p&gt;They will be part of a well-established integrated and multi-professional team that very much puts the patient at the centre of care (I-CARE) and be comfortable with communicating across secondary and primary care boundaries&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;We would welcome applications from individuals who are from underrepresented groups in the organisation &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Name :Jessie Dzingai&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Job title :Lead Respiratory Nurse&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Email address :Jessie.Dzingai@nhs.net&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Telephone numbern: 07500095460&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Interested candidates can contact the team to enquire about the expectations of the person and/or the post.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please contact Anthony Rafferty, Lead respiratory Physiotherpaist 07919575653 or Lead Nurse respiratory Specialist, Jessie Dzingai 07500095460&lt;/p&gt;
